{"tid":722183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【侵吞酬勞】蕭定一與張智霖續約 須保證對方3年收入共達1億元","createTime":"2018-06-29T09:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T15:36:17.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4d7d4bf73b00f4883c9ff7e67aeed96f0607f00a","tid":722183,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:18:18.000Z","msg":"藝人張智霖前女經理人涉擅改三份張的廣告合約，詐騙蕭定一旗下娛樂公司案，被告今出庭自辯講述工作時透露，張智霖在2013年9月會加盟公司簽三年合約時，公司須保證張每年收入須達1,000萬;及雙方簽續約，則公司須保證張於該3年內每年最少有3,000萬元收入，3年則達1億元。<br />\n<br />\n被告梁雅詩（43歲）稱，蕭定一為要她專心「跑數」，毋須她負責電影工作。而她為張與客戶洽談工作時，除需要依照張智霖之前講明，不會接影響印象如三級片、裸露及講粗口的工作條件外，磋商酬金時亦不可低於底線價，惟凡是不低於底價的工作，可由梁自行決定，亦由她負責簽合約，毋須向蕭及張滙報。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/171758_dcd092f6604d521cd925f33871b6e844.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F171758_dcd092f6604d521cd925f33871b6e844.png&h=34a4a6e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180629/58379392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180629%2F58379392&d=Zp%2FOZbqkgEy4%2Bn%2FMoifyyJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=2633e4d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180629%2F58379392&h=107ab897\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180629/58379392</a>"},{"pid":"6a2963af76a0426a8b9a001ff33d988654c6486a","tid":722183,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa5a9d72075edddbc806b327a321c3b0f48bdaa","tid":722183,"uid":52122,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:19:52.000Z","msg":"藝人真係最撚好搵既職業"},{"pid":"0af46e2f08ac190d8f0054622180dac28296ffae","tid":722183,"uid":29314,"like":10,"disli